WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Open OANDA:XAUUSD on the one hour chart with the PROSPER marker visible.

00:06.000 --> 00:12.000
Read the marker state first. It slows you down, but the checklist still decides.

00:12.000 --> 00:18.000
Box the Asian range from 0000 to 0700 UK time. Mark high, low, and midline.

00:18.000 --> 00:25.000
Judge the quality. More than eight updates or one candle dominating the box means no trade.

00:25.000 --> 00:32.000
Wait for the H1 candle close outside the range. A wick outside the box is not enough.

00:32.000 --> 00:39.000
After the close, plan entry, opposite-box stop, and the 2R target before any action.

00:39.000 --> 00:46.000
Journal the marker state, range quality, news check, decision, result in R, and lesson learned.
